commitResults.messageBody:
HistoryTracker class is responsible for managing the persistence of meal entries and meal options. Key features include:

* Saving and loading meal entries and meal options to/from CSV files
* Conversion between in-memory objects and CSV format

Additional changes:
* Added new CSV files for storing meal entries and options
* Modified existing classes (ChatParser, Meal, MealEntriesList, MealList) to integrate with HistoryTracker
